矩尺座γ、[[矩尺座δ|矩尺座δ]]、[[矩尺座ε|矩尺座ε]]和[[矩尺座η|矩尺座η]]四颗明亮恒星在黯淡星空组成方形<ref name="streicher">{{cite journal | last = Streicher  | first = Magda  | year = 2005  | title =  Deepsky Delights: Sparkling clusters in Norma | journal = Monthly Notes of the Astronomical Society of Southern Africa | volume = 64 | issue = 5–6  | pages = 107–09  | bibcode = 2005MNSSA..64..107S}}</ref>。[[矩尺座γ¹|矩尺座γ<sup>1</sup>]]和矩尺座γ<sup>2</sup>是[[雙星|光学双星]]，不属[[聯星|联星系]]。矩尺座γ<sup>2</sup>离地129±1[[光年|光年]]<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007">{{cite journal | first = F. | last = van Leeuwen | title = Validation of the New Hipparcos Reduction | journal = [[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | volume = 474 | issue = 2 | pages = 653–664 | year = 2007 | bibcode = 2007A&A...474..653V | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20078357 | arxiv = 0708.1752}}</ref>，是光谱等级G8III的黄巨星，约有2到2.5倍[[太阳质量|太阳质量]]，但已膨胀到十倍太阳直径，光度45倍。除矩尺座γ<sup>1</sup>外，矩尺座γ<sup>2</sup>还有十等伴星<ref name="kalergamma">{{cite web | first = James B. | last = Kaler | title = Gamma-2 Normae | work = Stars | publisher = University of Illinois | archive-date = 2020-07-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731231605/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gamma2nor.html | dead-url = no | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/gamma2nor.html | access-date = 2021-03-19 }}</ref>。矩尺座γ<sup>1</sup>是距地球约1500光年的黄白[[超巨星|超巨星]]<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007" />。矩尺座ε是[[聯星|光谱联星]]，离地530±20光年<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007" />，由两颗质量几乎相等、光谱等级均为B3V的[[B型主序星|蓝白主序星]]组成，两星围绕彼此以3.26天公转周期旋转。距两星22[[弧秒|弧秒]]还有第三颗星，亮度7.5视星等，估计是质量不及两颗主星的B类主序星，光谱等级B9V。<ref name="ncsbo">{{cite journal | last1 = Pourbaix | first1 = D. | last2 = Tokovinin | first2 = A.A. | last3 = Batten | first3 = A.H. | last4 = Fekel | first4 = F.C. | last5 = Hartkopf | first5 = W.I. | last6 = Levato | first6 = H. | last7 = Morell | first7 = N. I. | last8 = Torres | first8 = G. | last9 = Udry | first9 = S. | year = 2004 | title = SB9: The Ninth Catalogue of Spectroscopic Binary Orbits | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 424 | issue = 2 | bibcode = 2004A&A...424..727P | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20041213 | pages = 727–732 | arxiv = astro-ph/0406573}}</ref>4.65视星等的矩尺座η光谱等级G8III<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-19 | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Eta+Nor&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id | title = Eta Normae | work = SIMBAD Astronomical Database | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | archive-date = 2020-08-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805132853/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=Eta+Nor&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id }}</ref>，光度约为太阳66倍<ref name="Mcdonald">{{cite journal | last1 = McDonald | first1 = I. | last2 = Zijlstra | first2 = A. A. | last3 = Boyer | first3 = M. L. | year = 2012 | title = Fundamental Parameters and Infrared Excesses of Hipparcos Stars | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 427 | issue = 1 | pages = 343–357 | bibcode = 2012MNRAS.427..343M | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2012.21873.x | arxiv = 1208.2037}}</ref>。

[[矩尺座ι|矩尺座ι<sup>1</sup>]]包括多颗星体，其中两颗主星分别是5.2和5.76视星等，以26.9年轨道周期围绕彼此旋转，质量分别是太阳2.77和2.71倍<ref name="malkov">{{cite journal | last1 = Malkov | first1 = O. Yu  | last2 = Tamazian | first2 = V.S. | last3 = Docobo | first3 = J.A. | last4 = Chulkov | first4 = D.A. | year = 2012 | title = Dynamical Masses of a Selected Sample of Orbital Binaries | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 546 | id = A69 | pages = 5 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201219774 | bibcode =2012A&A...546A..69M}}</ref>，离地128±6光年<ref name="vanLeeuwen2007" />。第三颗星体光谱等级G8V，是8.02视星等的黄主序星<ref name="malkov" />。

[[矩尺座μ|矩尺座μ]]是光谱等级O9.7Iab的黄超巨星，距地球非常遥远<ref name="sota 2014">{{cite journal | last1 = Sota | first1 = A. | last2 = Maíz Apellániz | first2 = J. | last3 = Morrell | first3 = N.I. | last4 = Barbá | first4 = R.H. | last5 = Walborn | first5 = N.R. | last6 = Gamen | first6 = R.C. | last7 = Arias | first7 = J.I. | last8 = Alfaro | first8 = E.J. | year = 2014 | title = The Galactic O-Star Spectroscopic Survey (GOSSS). II. Bright Southern Stars | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Supplement | volume = 211 | issue = 1 | id = 10 | pages = 84 | doi = 10.1088/0067-0049/211/1/10 | bibcode = 2014ApJS..211...10S | arxiv = 1312.6222}}</ref>，光度在人类已知恒星中名列前芭，但因距离太远和[[宇宙塵埃|宇宙塵埃]]遮挡难以测量，估计光度达太阳25到100万倍，质量最高60倍，并以约50万倍光度和40倍质量几率最大<ref name="kalermu">{{cite web | first = James B. | last = Kaler | title = Mu Normae | work = Stars | publisher = University of Illinois | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/munor.html | date = 2010-07-30 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805090633/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/munor.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-05 }}</ref>。该星有可能是[[天鵝座α型變星|天鵝座α型變星]]，亮度在4.87到4.98视星等范围变化。[[矩尺座QU|矩尺座QU]]是炽热的蓝白变星，亮度以4.8天为周期在5.27至5.41视星等闪耀<ref name="AAVSOQU">{{cite web | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=20289 | title = QU Normae | last = Otero | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805172839/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=20289 | first = Sebastian Alberto | date = 2012-05-24 | work = The International Variable Star Index | archive-date = 2020-08-05 | publisher = American Association of Variable Star Observers | access-date = 2021-03-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[矩尺座R|矩尺座R]]在矩尺座η附近<ref name="arnold">{{cite book | last1 = Arnold | first1 = H.J.P. | last2 = Doherty | first2 = Paul | last3 = Moore | first3 = Patrick | title = The Photographic Atlas of the Stars | publisher = CRC Press | location = Boca Raton, Florida | year = 1999 | page = 176 | isbn = 978-0-750-30654-6 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&q="Ursa+Minor"+variable&pg=PA148&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=%22Ursa%20Minor%22%20variable&f=false | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411041613/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&q=%22Ursa+Minor%22+variable&pg=PA148&redir_esc=y#v=snippet&q=%22Ursa%20Minor%22%20variable&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>，是亮度以507.5天为周期在6.5至13.9视星等闪烁的[[刍藁变星|刍藁变星]]。矩尺座η和[[圆规座γ|圆规座γ]]之间中途位置的矩尺座T也是刍藁变星，<ref name="arnold" />亮度以244天为周期在6.2到13.6视星等范围变动<ref name="AAVSOT">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806020223/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=19963 | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=19963 | title = T Normae | last = Otero | first = Sebastian Alberto | date = 2011-05-19 | work = The International Variable Star Index | publisher = American Association of Variable Star Observers | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-06 }}</ref>。[[矩尺座S|矩尺座S]]是知名[[造父变星|造父变星]]，亮度以9.75411天为周期在6.12至6.77视星等变动<ref name="AAVSOS">{{cite web | publisher = American Association of Variable Star Observers | url = https://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=19962 | title = S Normae | last = Watson | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200805051939/http://www.aavso.org/vsx/index.php?view=detail.top&oid=19962 | first = Christopher | date = 2010-01-04 | work = The International Variable Star Index | access-date = 2021-03-19 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-08-05 }}</ref>。该星位于[[NGC天體表|NGC 6087]][[疏散星团|疏散星团]]中央，是光谱等级F8-G0Ib的黄白超巨星，拥有6.3倍太阳质量。矩尺座S还是联星，伴星是光谱等级B9.5V的蓝白主序星，质量为太阳2.4倍。<ref name="evans13">{{cite journal | last1 = Evans | first1 = Nancy Remage | last2 = Bond | first2 = Howard E. | last3 = Schaefer | first3 = Gail H. | last4 = Mason | first4 = Brian D. | last5 = Karovska | first5 = Margarita | last6 = Tingle | first6 = Evan | year = 2013 | title = Binary Cepheids: Separations and Mass Ratios in 5M ⊙ Binaries | journal = [[天文期刊|Astronomical Journal]] | volume = 146 | issue = 4 | pages = 93, 10 pp | arxiv = 1307.7123 | doi = 10.1088/0004-6256/146/4/93 | bibcode = 2013AJ....146...93E}}</ref>[[阿佩普_(恆星系統)|阿佩普]]离地约八千光年，是两颗[[沃爾夫–拉葉星|沃爾夫–拉葉星]]组成的联星系，有可能是长[[伽玛射线暴|伽玛射线暴]]的源头，如果确是如此，这就是人类在银河系发现的第一个长伽玛射线暴源头<ref>{{cite web | last = Weule | first = Genelle | title = Spectacular cosmic pinwheel is a 'ticking bomb' set to blast gamma rays across the Milky Way | website = ABC News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124215714/https://www.abc.net.au/news/science/2018-11-20/wolf-rayet-star-may-blast-milky-way-with-gamma-ray-burst/10506316 | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | url = https://www.abc.net.au/news/science/2018-11-20/wolf-rayet-star-may-blast-milky-way-with-gamma-ray-burst/10506316 | date = 2018-11-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

人类在银河系发现十颗[[再发新星|再发新星]]，其中[[矩尺座IM|矩尺座IM]]曾于1920和2002年爆发，亮度从最低的18.3视星等增至8.5。1920年爆发后人类对该星观测不足，星体有可能在2002年前再度爆发。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Schaefer | first = Bradley E. | year = 2010 | title = Comprehensive Photometric Histories of All Known Galactic Recurrent Novae | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Supplement | volume = 187 | issue = 2 | pages = 275–373 | doi = 10.1088/0067-0049/187/2/275 | bibcode = 2010ApJS..187..275S | arxiv = 0912.4426}}</ref>矩尺座有两颗黯淡的十等[[北冕座R型變星|北冕座R型變星]]，分别是[[矩尺座RT|矩尺座RT]]和[[矩尺座RZ|矩尺座RZ]]，估计是两颗[[白矮星|白矮星]]合并而成的罕见[[致密星|衰退星体]]，亮度因星体喷发大量碳尘而按周期衰减数级<ref name="ASAS">{{cite arXiv | eprint = 1211.2475v2 | author1 = Tisserand | author2 = Clayton | author3 = Welch | author4 = Pilecki | author5 = Wyrzykowski | author6 = Kilkenny | title = The Ongoing Pursuit of R Coronae Borealis Stars: ASAS-3 Survey Strikes Again | class = astro-ph.SR | year = 2012}}</ref>。黯淡的16等星[[矩尺座QV|矩尺座QV]]离地1.5至2万光年，属高质量[[X射线联星|X射线联星]]，由[[中子星|中子星]]围绕约20倍太阳质量的蓝色超巨星组成。高质量恒星的[[星风|星风]]由中子星磁极吸引，形成吸积柱并产生X射线<ref name="Hemphill 2014">{{cite journal | last1 = Hemphill | first1 = Paul B. | last2 = Rothschild | first2 = Richard E. | last3 = Markowitz | first3 = Alex | last4 = Fürst | first4 = Felix | last5 = Pottschmidt | first5 = Katja | last6 = Wilms | first6 = Jörn | year = 2014 | title = A Clumpy Stellar Wind and Luminosity-dependent Cyclotron Line Revealed by the First Suzaku Observation of the High-mass X-Ray Binary 4U 1538-522 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 792 | issue = 1 | pages = 15 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/792/1/14 | bibcode = 2014ApJ...792...14H | arxiv = 1407.1028}}</ref>。矩尺座QX距地球1.9万光年<ref name="Güver 2010" />，是活跃的小质量X射线联星，由中子星和尺寸与温度都小于太阳的伴星组成<ref name="Wachter 2002">{{cite journal | last1 = Wachter | first1 = Stephanie | last2 = Hoard | first2 = D. W. | last3 = Bailyn | first3 = Charles D. | last4 = Corbel | first4 = Stephane | last5 = Kaaret | first5 = Philip E. | year = 2002 | title = A Closer Look at the Soft X-ray Transient X1608-52 : Long-term Optical\/X-ray Observations | journal = Astrophys. J. | volume = 568 | issue = 2 | pages = 901–911 | doi = 10.1086/339034 | arxiv = astro-ph/0112465 | bibcode = 2002ApJ...568..901W}}</ref>。该中子星质量为太阳1.74±0.14倍，半径仅9.3±1.0公里<ref name="Güver 2010">{{cite journal | last1 = Güver | first1 = Tolga | last2 = Özel | first2 = Feryal | last3 = Cabrera-Lavers | first3 = Antonio | last4 = Wroblewski | first4 = Patricia | title = The Distance, Mass, and Radius of the Neutron Star in 4U 1608-52 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 712 | issue = 2 | pages = 964–973 | year = 2010 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/712/2/964 | bibcode = 2010ApJ...712..964G | arxiv = 0811.3979}}</ref>。[[RCW_103|RCW 103]][[超新星遗迹|超新星遗迹]]中央的中子星[[1E161348-5055|1E161348-5055]]离地一万光年，约有两千年历史，是6.67小时周期的[[X射线|X射线]]源，该星自转速度异常缓慢，同已有数百万年历史的星体类似<ref>{{cite journal | first1 = A. | last1 = De Luca | last2 = Caraveo | first2 = P. A. | last3 = Mereghetti | first3 = S. | last4 = Tiengo | first4 = A. | last5 = Bignami | first5 = G. F. | date = 2006-08-11 | title = A Long-Period, Violently Variable X-ray Source in a Young Supernova Remnant | journal = Science | volume = 313 | issue = 5788 | pages = 814–17 | doi = 10.1126/science.1129185 | arxiv = astro-ph/0607173 | pmid = 16825535 | bibcode = 2006Sci...313..814D}}</ref>。[[SGR_J1550-5418|SGR J1550-5418]]是[[軟γ射線重複爆發源|軟γ射線重複爆發源]]，即发射伽马射线耀斑的[[磁星|磁星]]<ref>{{cite journal | title = Time Resolved Spectroscopy of SGR J1550-5418 Bursts Detected with Fermi/Gamma-Ray Burst Monitor | last1 = Younes | first1 = G. | last2 = Kouveliotou | first2 = C. | last3 = van der Horst | first3 = A. J. | last4 = Baring | first4 = M. G. | last5 = Granot | first5 = J. | last6 = Watts | first6 = A. L. | last7 = Bhat | first7 = P. N. | last8 = Collazzi | first8 = A. | last9 = Gehrels | first9 = N. | last10 = Gorgone | first10 = N. | last11 = Göğüş | first11 = E. | last12 = Gruber | first12 = D. | last13 = Grunblatt | first13 = S. | last14 = Huppenkothen | first14 = D. | last15 = Kaneko | first15 = Y. | last16 = von Kienlin | first16 = A. | last17 = van der Klis | first17 = M. | last18 = Lin | first18 = L. | last19 = Mcenery | first19 = J. | last20 = van Putten | first20 = T. | last21 = Wijers | first21 = R. A. M. J. | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 785 | issue = 1 | id = 52 | pages = 11 | year = 2014 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/785/1/52 | bibcode = 2014ApJ...785...52Y | arxiv = 1402.6015 | hdl = 1911/75890 | url = https://pure.uva.nl/ws/files/2181967/156763_Time_Resolved_Spectroscopy.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127114316/https://pure.uva.nl/ws/files/2181967/156763_Time_Resolved_Spectroscopy.pdf | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | access-date = 2021-03-19 }}</ref>，距地球约三万光年，自转周期仅2.07秒，是人类所知自转最快的磁星<ref>{{cite web | url = https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0902/10gammarays/ | title = ESA News Release: Swift, Fermi probe fireworks from flaring gamma-ray star | date = 2009-02-10 | work = Spaceflight Now | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211001545/https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0902/10gammarays/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | access-date = 2021-03-19 }}</ref>。[[XTE_J1550-564|XTE J1550-564]]也是X射线联星，由质量约十倍太阳的黑洞和橙色冷却捐赠星组成，其中的黑洞是[[微類星體|微類星體]]，[[相对论性喷流|喷出的物质气流]]很可能形成[[吸积盘|吸积盘]]<ref name="Steiner 2011">{{cite journal | last1 = Steiner | first1 = James F. | last2 = Reis | first2 = Rubens C. | last3 = McClintock | first3 = Jeffrey E. | last4 = Narayan | first4 = Ramesh | last5 = Remillard | first5 = Ronald A. | last6 = Orosz | first6 = Jerome A. | last7 = Gou | first7 = Lijun | last8 = Fabian | first8 = Andrew C. | last9 = Torres | first9 = Manuel A. P. | year = 2011 | title = The spin of the black hole microquasar XTE J1550-564 via the continuum-fitting and Fe-line methods | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 416 | issue = 2 | pages = 941–958 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2011.19089.x | bibcode = 2011MNRAS.416..941S | arxiv = 1010.1013}}</ref>。

矩尺座四个恒星系有[[太陽系外行星|行星]]。[[HD_330075|HD 330075]]是离地约164光年的類太陽恆星，周围旋转的[[熱木星|熱木星]]公转周期仅3.4天。这是人类利用[[高精度徑向速度行星搜索器|高精度徑向速度行星搜索器]][[光谱仪|光谱仪]]发现的第一颗行星，消息在2004年公布。<ref name="Pepe2004">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20040389 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124070900/https://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=standard&Itemid=129&url=%2Farticles%2Faa%2Ffull%2F2004%2F31%2Faa0389-04%2Faa0389-04.html | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | last4 = Benz | url = https://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=com_article&access=standard&Itemid=129&url=/articles/aa/full/2004/31/aa0389-04/aa0389-04.html | title = The HARPS search for southern extra-solar planets I. HD 330075 b: A new 'hot Jupiter' | last1 = Pepe | first1 = F. | last2 = Mayor | first2 = M. | last3 = Queloz | first3 = D. | first4 = W. | last5 = Bonfils | first5 = X. | last6 = Bouchy | first6 = F. | last7 = Lo Curto | first7 = G. | last8 = Lovis | first8 = C. | last9 = Mégevand | first9 = D. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 423 | issue = 1 | pages = 385–389 | year = 2004 | arxiv = astro-ph/0405252 | bibcode = 2004A&A...423..385P | access-date = 2022-01-19 }}</ref>距地球168±7光年的[[HD_148156|HD 148156]]尺寸和温度都略超太阳，有尺寸类似木星的行星，公转周期2.8年<ref name="Naef2010">{{cite journal | title = The HARPS Search for Southern Extrasolar Planets XXIII. 8 Planetary Companions to Low-activity Solar-type Stars | url = https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2010/15/aa13616-09/aa13616-09.html | last1 = Naef | first1 = D. | last2 = Mayor | first2 = M. | last3 = Curto | first3 = G. Lo | last4 = Bouchy | first4 = F. | last5 = Lovis | first5 = C. | last6 = Moutou | first6 = C. | last7 = Benz | first7 = W. | last8 = Pepe | first8 = F. | last9 = Queloz | first9 = D. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 523 | page = A15 | year = 2010 | arxiv = 1008.4600 | bibcode = 2010A&A...523A..15N | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/200913616 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | archive-date = 2016-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160812043539/http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full_html/2010/15/aa13616-09/aa13616-09.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[HD_143361|HD 143361]]是类太阳恒星与黯淡[[红矮星|红矮星]]组成的联星系，两星相隔30.9[[天文单位|天文单位]]，另有约三倍木星质量的行星以1057±20天轨道周期围绕类太阳恒星旋转<ref name="MAGELLAN">{{cite journal | last1 = Minniti | first1 = Dante | last2 = Butler | first2 = R. Paul | last3 = López-Morales | first3 = Mercedes | last4 = Shectman | first4 = Stephen A. | last5 = Adams | first5 = Fred C. | last6 = Arriagada | first6 = Pamela | last7 = Boss | first7 = Alan P. | last8 = Chambers | first8 = John E. | title = Low-Mass Companions for Five Solar-Type Stars From the Magellan Planet Search Program | journal = [[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] | year = 2009 | volume = 693 | issue = 2 | pages = 1424–1430 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637X/693/2/1424 | bibcode = 2009ApJ...693.1424M | arxiv = 0810.5348}}</ref>。[[HD_142415|HD 142415]]离地约113光年，拥有尺寸接近木星的行星，公转周期约386天<ref name="Mayor2004">{{cite journal | url = https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full/2004/07/aa0250/aa0250.html | title = The CORALIE Survey for Southern Extra-solar Planets XII. Orbital Solutions for 16 Extra-solar Planets Discovered with CORALIE | last1 = Mayor | first1 = M. | last2 = Udry | first2 = S. | last3 = Naef | first3 = D. | last4 = Pepe | first4 = F. | last5 = Queloz | first5 = D. | last6 = Santos | first6 = N. C. | last7 = Burnet | first7 = M. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 415 | issue = 1 | pages = 391–402 | year = 2004 | arxiv = astro-ph/0310316 | bibcode = 2004A&A...415..391M | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210130183205/https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/full/2004/07/aa0250/aa0250.html | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20034250 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-01-30 | access-date = 2021-03-19 }}</ref>。

