位于银河范围的矩尺座富含[[星团|星团]]等[[深空天體|深空天體]]<ref name="arnold" />，其中包括八个能用双筒望远镜观测的疏散星团<ref name="mobberly">{{cite book | last = Mobberly | first = Martin | title = The Caldwell Objects and How to Observe Them | location = New York, New York | isbn = 978-1-4419-0325-9 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=amPrWoOWgHcC&pg=PA186&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 2009 | publisher = Springer | pages = 186–187 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411041725/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=amPrWoOWgHcC&pg=PA186&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。5.4视星等的[[NGC_6087|NGC 6087]]比矩尺座其他疏散星团都亮，位于星座东南角，在[[南門二|南門二]]和[[天壇座ζ|天壇座ζ]]之间。星团约有一亿年历史，离地约3300光年，直径约14光年，内部又以造父变星[[矩尺座S|矩尺座S]]最亮，<ref name="mobberly" />但附近恒星众多所以不明显，用放大150倍的十厘米望远镜能看到约36颗星体<ref name="bakich2010" />。[[矩尺座κ|矩尺座κ]]以北0.4°的[[NGC_6067|NGC 6067]][[面亮度|面亮度]]5.6，同样因附近恒星众多而不明显<ref name="bakich2010">{{cite book | first = Michael E. | last = Bakich | year = 2010 | pages = 190–191 | title = 1001 Celestial Wonders to See Before You Die: The Best Sky Objects for Star Gazers | isbn = 978-1-4419-1777-5 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | url = https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=qEhpS7d5ZdAC&pg=PA191&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | series = Patrick Moore's Practical Astronomy Series | publisher = Springer | location = New York, New York | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411041727/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=qEhpS7d5ZdAC&pg=PA191&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。估计该星团约有1.02亿年历史，质量为太阳891倍<ref name="aaa477_1_165">{{cite journal | last1 = Piskunov | first1 = A. E. | last2 = Schilbach | first2 = E. | last3 = Kharchenko | first3 = N. V. | last4 = Röser | first4 = S. | last5 = Scholz | first5 = R.-D. | title = Tidal Radii and Masses of Open Clusters | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 477 | issue = 1 | date = 2008-01-01 | pages = 165–172 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20078525 | bibcode = 2008A&A...477..165P}}</ref>，其中已发现矩尺座QZ和矩尺座V340两颗造父变星<ref name="majaess">{{cite journal | last1 = Majaess | first1 = D. | last2 = Sturch | first2 = L. | last3 = Moni Bidin | first3 = C. | last4 = Soto | first4 = M. | last5 = Gieren | first5 = W. | last6 = Cohen | first6 = R. | last7 = Mauro | first7 = F. | last8 = Geisler | first8 = D. | last9 = Bonatto | first9 = C. | last10 = Borissova | first10 = J. | last11 = Minniti | first11 = D. | last12 = Turner | first12 = D. | last13 = Lane | first13 = D. | last14 = Madore | first14 = B. | last15 = Carraro | first15 = G. | last16 = Berdnikov | first16 = L. | title = Anchors for the Cosmic Distance Scale: the Cepheid QZ Normae in the Open Cluster NGC 6067 | journal = Astrophysics and Space Science | volume = 347 | issue = 1 | pages = 61–70 | date = 2013-08 | doi = 10.1007/s10509-013-1495-1 | bibcode = 2013Ap&SS.347...61M | arxiv = 1305.3914}}</ref>。距地球四千光年的[[NGC_6134|NGC 6134]]合并亮度7.2视星等，不及上述疏散星团，此外还有[[NGC_6031|NGC 6031]]、[[NGC_5999|NGC 5999]]、6.7视星等的[[NGC_6167|NGC 6167]]，矩尺座γ附近的[[NGC_6115|NGC 6115]]<ref name="streicher" />。
