矩尺座γ<sup>1</sup>西北偏西约五度夜空的[[行星状星云|行星状星云]][[沙普利1|沙普利1]]离地约4900光年，因呈戒指状又名“细指环星云”，估计是直接对准地球的圆柱形，约有8700年历史<ref name="Jones 2012">{{cite journal | last1 = Jones | first1 = D. | last2 = Mitchell | first2 = D. L. | last3 = Lloyd | first3 = M. | last4 = Pollacco | first4 = D. | last5 = O'Brien | first5 = T. J. | last6 = Meaburn | first6 = J. | last7 = Vaytet | first7 = N. M. H. | year = 2012 | title = The Morphology and Kinematics of the Fine Ring Nebula, Planetary Nebula Sp 1, and the Shaping Influence of its Binary Central Star | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 420 | issue = 3 | pages = 2271–2279 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2966.2011.20192.x | bibcode = 2012MNRAS.420.2271J | arxiv = 1111.2860}}</ref>。星云合并亮度13.6视星等，平均面亮度13.9视星等，中央是14.03视星等的白矮星。[[Mz_1|Mz 1]]是[[雙極星雲|双极]]行星状行云，估计是沙漏状，与地球观测角度有一定倾斜，距地球约3500光年。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Monteiro | first1 = Hektor | last2 = Schwarz | first2 = Hugo E. | last3 = Gruenwald | first3 = Ruth | last4 = Guenthner | first4 = Katherine | last5 = Heathcote | first5 = Steve R. | title = Three-Dimensional Photoionization Structure and Distances of Planetary Nebulae. II. Menzel 1 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | date = 2005 | volume = 620 | issue = 1 | pages = 321–29 | bibcode = 2005ApJ...620..321M | doi = 10.1086/426809 |arxiv = astro-ph/0410496}}</ref>[[螞蟻星雲|螞蟻星雲]]形似蚂蚁且外形复杂，至少可见四道外喷气流和两大裂片<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Santander-García | first1 = M. | last2 = Corradi | first2 = R. L. M. | last3 = Balick | first3 = B. | last4 = Mampaso | first4 = A. | title = Menzel 3: Dissecting the Ant | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | date = 2004 | volume = 426 | issue = 1 | pages = 185–194 | bibcode = 2004A&A...426..185S | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20041147 | arxiv = astro-ph/0406551}}</ref>。

